org.hps.conditions.run

Class RunRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.conditions.run.RunRange

  • public final class RunRange
extends Object
    Used with the RunSpreadsheet to find ranges of runs where columns have the same values so they can be assigned a conditions record with a run start and end range.

    Bad rows such as ones without run numbers or with invalid data values are skipped and not included in a range.
